      <title>特朗普称仍考虑征收 10% 关税，中国股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/chinese-stocks-fall-after-trump-says-10-tariffs-still-on-table</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他威胁对中国商品征收 10% 的关税仍在考虑中，并且可能在下个月实施，此后中国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/chinese-stocks-fall-after-trump-says-10-tariffs-still-on-table</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 02:29:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普重申对华关税威胁后大豆价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/soybeans-decline-after-trump-reiterates-china-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示正在考虑对中国征收关税，这引发了人们对两大经济体之间爆发贸易战的担忧，芝加哥大豆期货价格下跌。小麦和玉米期货价格也下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/soybeans-decline-after-trump-reiterates-china-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Brookfield 接近以 9.5 亿美元收购 Divvy Homes</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/brookfield-nears-950-million-purchase-of-divvy-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 即将达成协议，通过收购初创公司 Divvy Homes，以约 9.5 亿美元的价格购买 3,800 套单户出租住宅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/brookfield-nears-950-million-purchase-of-divvy-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:49:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Robeco：亚洲软件将受益于人工智能推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-22/asia-software-stands-to-benefit-from-ai-push-robeco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robeco 的 Vicki Chi 表示，特朗普总统推动的人工智能投资将进一步支持亚洲技术供应链，该供应链已经“表现得非常非常好”。Chi 告诉彭博电视台，人工智能正处于“转折点”，因为“今年，随着人工智能的出现，我们将越来越多地看到消费者感受到这种变化。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-22/asia-software-stands-to-benefit-from-ai-push-robeco</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:44:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税威胁引发贸易战担忧，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对中国征收关税，并表示正在考虑对加拿大和墨西哥征收高额关税，这引发了人们对多条战线贸易战的担忧，导致油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 23:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能希望抵消关税担忧，股市小幅上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 领导下增加人工智能支出的乐观情绪抵消了对中国关税影响的担忧，亚洲股市小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度安得拉邦部长奈杜谈投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/india-s-andhra-pradesh-s-minister-naidu-on-investment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度南部邦安得拉邦首席部长 Chandrababu Naidu 与彭博社的 Menaka Doshi 坐下来讨论该国的全球投资机会以及该邦的绿色能源投资计划。他在瑞士达沃斯世界经济论坛间隙发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/india-s-andhra-pradesh-s-minister-naidu-on-investment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 17:36:09 GMT</pubDate>
